    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5279-Essence-of-Bhagwat-Gita-2nd-Chapter.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Essence of Bhagwat Gita: 2nd Chapter&#34; /&gt;
      
