&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Essence of Bhagwat Gita: 2nd Chapter 
    &lt;div id=&#34;the-essence-of-bhagwat-gita-2nd-chapter&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
