&lt;p&gt;The second chapter of Bhagavad Gita is &amp;ldquo;Sankhya Yoga&amp;rdquo; - The Yoga of Analysis. This chapter is one of the longest in the Bhagavad Gita, it has 72 slokas (verses). Sometimes people say if you understand this chapter throughly then you don&amp;rsquo;t need any other chapter, if you don&amp;rsquo;t have time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
