There are people for whom it is a useless time waste,  &lt;br&gt;
better do something more important.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is the English word meditation the same as Dhyanam word of Samskrut?  &lt;br&gt;
Then what about Japam, Dharana, and Samadhi in English?  &lt;br&gt;
What is the English word for Samadhi?  &lt;br&gt;
If no word then what do you think  &lt;br&gt;
why this word is missing in mapping to the English dictionary?  &lt;br&gt;
Any deeper meaning?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
