&lt;p&gt;What is the mind? Don’t mistake it for the brain.  &lt;br&gt;
The brain is physical and it is located inside the physical head.  &lt;br&gt;
A perceiving mind is not a matter, but it matters a lot.  &lt;br&gt;
This non-matter which matters is not located in one place.  &lt;br&gt;
The whole body is the home of the mind.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
